---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog | Insights για Web Development
description: Άρθρα, οδηγοί και insights για κατασκευή ιστοσελίδων, SEO, performance optimization και digital marketing στην Ελλάδα.
---

<section class="section bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Blog & Insights</h1>
      <p class="section-subtitle mx-auto text-center">Πρακτικές συμβουλές για ιστοσελίδες, eshop, SEO και performance</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
      <article class="card group flex flex-col transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="flex-1 p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            {% if post.data.category %}
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-brand/10 text-brand">
              {{ post.data.category }}
            </span>
            {% endif %}
            {% if post.data.readingTime %}
            <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">{{ post.data.readingTime }} min</span>
            {% endif %}
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="block">
              {{ post.data.title }}
            </a>
          </h2>

          {% if post.data.excerpt %}
          <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 text-sm line-clamp-3">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-4 border-t border-slate-100 mt-auto">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-slate-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 font-semibold text-xs">
                MT
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">{{ post.data.author | default("Michael Topouzis") }}</span>
            </div>
            <time class="text-xs text-slate-400" datetime="{{ post.date | dateIso }}">
              {{ post.date | dateFormat }}
            </time>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% else %}
      <div class="col-span-full text-center py-12">
        <p class="text-slate-500">Δεν υπάρχουν άρθρα ακόμα. Έρχονται σύντομα!</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section bg-slate-900">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white">Θέλετε να λαμβάνετε τα νέα μας;</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 max-w-xl mx-auto">Εγγραφείτε στο newsletter μας για tips, case studies και web development insights.</p>
    <form class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center max-w-md mx-auto" action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID" method="POST">
      <label for="newsletter-email-blog" class="sr-only">Email</label>
      <input
        type="email"
        id="newsletter-email-blog"
        name="email"
        required
        placeholder="you@example.com"
        class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-white placeholder-slate-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-brand focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand"
      >
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary whitespace-nowrap">
        Εγγραφή
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
